@* قائِمَة مُنسَدِلَة. selected عَلى الـ option المُطابِق ⇒ تَعبِئَة مَجّانِيَّة. *@

<div class="mb-3">
    <label class="form-label">
        @(Definition.LabelAr ?? Definition.Label)
        @if (Definition.Required) { <span class="text-danger">*</span> }
    </label>
    <select class="form-select"
            value="@AsString(Value)"
            @onchange="@(e => OnChange(e.Value?.ToString()))">
        <option value="">— اختَر —</option>
        @foreach (var opt in Definition.Options)
        {
            <option value="@opt.Value">@(opt.LabelAr ?? opt.Label)</option>
        }
        @if (!string.IsNullOrEmpty(_legacyValue))
        {
            <option value="@_legacyValue">@_legacyValue (قَديم)</option>
        }
    </select>
</div>

@code {
    [Parameter, EditorRequired] public AttributeFieldDefinition Definition { get; set; } = default!;
    [Parameter] public object? Value { get; set; }
    [Parameter] public EventCallback<object?> ValueChanged { get; set; }

    private string? _legacyValue;

    protected override void OnParametersSet()
    {
        var current = AsString(Value);
        _legacyValue = !string.IsNullOrEmpty(current)
                       && !Definition.Options.Any(o => string.Equals(o.Value, current, StringComparison.OrdinalIgnoreCase))
            ? current : null;
    }

    private static string AsString(object? v) => v?.ToString() ?? "";

    private Task OnChange(string? v) => ValueChanged.InvokeAsync(string.IsNullOrEmpty(v) ? null : v);
}
